Gold price on Saturday, November 2, 2019
02 Nov 2019, 09:30 by Walaa Abdel Karim
Gold prices stabilized in the trading today, Saturday, November 2, 2019 within the local markets on Friday highs by about 4 pounds per gram, recording the price of the 21-gram gram most prevalent in the local markets 677 pounds. The price of a gram of 18-carat gold ranged between 579 and 580 pounds, The price of a gram of 24-carat gold ranged from 771 to 774 pounds, and the gold pound recorded a price between 5400 and 5416 pounds;
